WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.266 --> 00:00:09.400
He actually stepped on the future

2
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:11.833
What are you doing?

3
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:19.200
Still that little brat

4
00:00:19.266 --> 00:00:21.700
People get angry when they move his things

5
00:00:21.766 --> 00:00:24.133
At first, I wished I could come to his room

6
00:00:24.133 --> 00:00:25.166
What about cleaning up?

7
00:00:28.266 --> 00:00:31.300
Mr. Zhang, my favorite snack is good

8
00:00:33.766 --> 00:00:35.966
I can do it, please

9
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:38.933
After all, I took care of you for so many years before

10
00:00:38.933 --> 00:00:40.666
It's not easy

11
00:00:42.733 --> 00:00:43.966
Thanks.

12
00:00:49.700 --> 00:00:53.100
Little brat, you like my fried rice best

13
00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:54.900
See if I don't take you down

14
00:00:54.900 --> 00:00:57.200
The taste is exactly the same as Lin Shi's and mine

15
00:00:57.200 --> 00:01:00.600
But how could Chen Lin even taste the same?

16
00:01:01.466 --> 00:01:02.966
Who are you?

17
00:01:03.533 --> 00:01:04.900
Of course I am Chen Lin.

18
00:01:05.300 --> 00:01:07.200
Who does Xiao Jiang always think it is?

19
00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:11.166
Don't play dumb. I've worked with tons of top chefs

20
00:01:11.166 --> 00:01:12.566
Trying to restore the taste

21
00:01:12.566 --> 00:01:14.866
None of these succeeded.

22
00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.300
Of course, Aunt Lin taught me to do it.

23
00:01:18.066 --> 00:01:21.433
He said he wanted to capture the hearts of men

24
00:01:21.466 --> 00:01:23.300
You have to capture his stomach first

25
00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:26.800
How about Mr. Xiao Jiang?

26
00:01:27.066 --> 00:01:28.866
Have you been captured by me?

27
00:01:33.133 --> 00:01:35.966
Miss Chen Lin wants to capture my heart

28
00:01:36.533 --> 00:01:37.600
Why is that?

29
00:01:37.966 --> 00:01:40.700
A man like Mr. Jiang

30
00:01:40.866 --> 00:01:42.600
Who wouldn't want to?

31
00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.433
So?

32
00:01:44.766 --> 00:01:47.400
Miss Chen Lin has taken a fancy to me

33
00:01:47.466 --> 00:01:48.766
Of course it is

34
00:01:54.566 --> 00:01:58.366
Why don't I take a shower now?

